## Key Flux Commands for This Flow

```bash
# Check if source-controller pulled the latest commit
flux get sources git

# Check HelmRelease status
flux get helmreleases

# Force a manual reconcile (don't wait for interval)
flux reconcile helmrelease demo-app-flux

# Check detailed status
kubectl describe helmrelease demo-app-flux -n flux-system

# Watch pods come up
watch kubectl get pods -n default
```

---

## Important: What Triggers a Flux Sync

| Change Made | Flux Syncs? | Why |
|---|---|---|
| values.yaml changed + Chart.yaml version bumped | YES | New chart version detected |
| values.yaml changed only (no version bump) | NO | ReconcileStrategy: ChartVersion |
| New commit pushed (any file) | Partial | source-controller updates, helm-controller checks version |
| Manual kubectl scale | NO self-heal | Helm sees no chart change |
| kubectl delete deployment | YES self-heal | Inventory detects missing resource |

